jettyHttpComponent.setResponseHeaderSize(51202);&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But there is no effect;then I checked the camel-jetty.jar&apos;s source,and found in JettyHttpComponent.createSocketConnector:&lt;br/&gt;
if (responseHeaderSize != null) &lt;/p&gt;
{
            answer.setResponseBufferSize(responseHeaderSize);
        }</description>
